description:
Don't miss the 'Girlfriend' Trailer for The Fantastic Four: First Steps, the latest installment in the MCU distributed by Marvel Studios. The Fantastic Four: First Steps is in theaters on July 25.
The Fantastic Four: First Steps stars Pedro Pascal, Vanessa Kirby, Joseph Quinn, Ebon Moss-Bachrach, Ralph Ineson, and Julia Garner. The Fantastic Four: First Steps opens in theaters on July 25, 2025.
Set against the vibrant backdrop of a 1960s-inspired, retro- futuristic world, Marvel Studios’ The Fantastic Four: First Steps introduces Marvel’s First Family—Reed Richards/Mister Fantastic (Pedro Pascal), Sue Storm/Invisible Woman (Vanessa Kirby), Johnny Storm/Human Torch (Joseph Quinn) and Ben Grimm/The Thing (Ebon Moss-Bachrach) as they face their most daunting challenge yet. Forced to balance their roles as heroes with the strength of their family bond, they must defend Earth from a ravenous space god called Galactus (Ralph Ineson) and his enigmatic Herald, Silver Surfer (Julia Garner). title: The Fantastic Four: First Steps - Official 'Girlfriend' Trailer

author: IGN
description: In all of pop culture there are few characters more globally recognizable than Superman. With a comic debut in the 30s and countless radio, tv and big screen appearances in the decades since, there have been plenty of actors don the cape and tights of the last son of Krypton. But how many of them have gotten it right? Let's take a look at all the live action Kal-El's over the decades and breakdown what it takes to be a good Superman.
title: Who Is The Greatest Superman?

author: IGN
description:
Finding the perfect gaming keyboard doesn't have to break the bank or leave you overwhelmed by countless options. In this guide, Michael Higham breaks down our top picks from budget-friendly to premium gaming keyboards, covering everything from mechanical switches to Hall Effect magnetic technology. Whether you're looking for a reliable sub-$50 option like the Keychron C3 Pro or ready to invest in premium features with the SteelSeries Apex Pro Gen 3, we've tested and reviewed each keyboard to help you find the perfect fit for your gaming setup.
From compact 60% layouts to full-sized functionality, we explore different switch types, connectivity options, and key features that matter most to gamers. Our picks include standout keyboards from trusted brands like Keychron, Logitech, and SteelSeries, each offering unique advantages whether you prioritize customization, build quality, or pure performance.
